item.title: CVE-2023-39224|2024-08-02T18:02:06.563Z -- tp-link -- archer%20c5
item.description: Archer C5 firmware all versions and Archer C7 firmware versions prior to 'Archer C7(JP)_V2_230602' allow a network-adjacent authenticated attacker to execute arbitrary OS commands. Note that Archer C5 is no longer supported, therefore the update for this product is not provided.
